Description:
The Park-Side Lifestyle You Deserve
For Sale By Auction Saturday November 16th @ 11am
Life is just about to get a whole lot better.Have you ever wanted to live a peaceful, park-side lifestyle with the convenience of being close to the city and countless amenities? If so, this property is perfect for you.
Wake up to natural greenery and bird tweeting with this afternoon sun-lit apartment providing a 1960s boutique gem in the best location in Melbourne, offering a spacious one bedroom apartment with character features and gorgeous city views across the road from Yarra Bend Parklands and Merri Creek trailsand it comes with a single garage and additional car space!
Key features:
- Captivating city views;
- Large open plan living, high ceilings and meals area with so much natural light from large windows;
- Well equipped kitchen with freestanding oven/cooktop with rangehood;
- Secured pull-up garage with additional car space;
- Double brick wall construction with the 2nd level rear of the apartment all to yourself;
- Sun-drenched bedroom with built-in-robes;
- White and bright en-suite bathroom with laundry facilities;
- Separate shared laundry space;
- Panel heater;
- Secure entry.
A hidden Melbourne secret, this location provides such a serene park-side lifestyle whilst you are only moments from Clifton Hill Train Station, Spensley's Wine Bar, Dirty Apron Café, Uncle Drews Café, Capital City Trail, Spensley Street Primary School, Queens Parade shopping strip and much much more.
Live the park-side lifestyle you deserve.
